<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 via-blue-300 to-blue-500 dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-800 dark:to-gray-700 min-h-screen">
<%- include("partials/navbar.ejs") %>
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-10 p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-200 mb-4">About GeoFacts</h1>
  <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">GeoFacts is an interactive world explorer dashboard that lets you discover country facts, weather, air quality, and track your travels. Mark countries as visited, add to your wishlist, and keep notes for each place you dream of visiting!</p>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200">
    <li>Interactive world map with country info</li>
    <li>Weather and air quality data</li>
    <li>User accounts and travel tracking</li>
    <li>Wishlist and notes for each country</li>
    <li>Beautiful, responsive design</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Created with ❤️ using Node.js, Express, PostgreSQL, Leaflet.js, and Tailwind CSS.</p>
</div> 
</body>
</html>